<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17275</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>劳拉、卢克、奥利维亚、卡洛斯、凯蒂和乔伊都穿得厚厚的，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17275</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>走在放学回家的路上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19833</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23632</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“贝柔老师跟你说了什么？” 劳拉问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23632</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29618</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她说我们昨天的表现不像领袖。” 乔伊伤心地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29618</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她是对的。当柯提思老师叫我们时，我们不应该不理他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36034</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“贝柔老师也跟我谈了。” 奥利维亚说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她说向父母示威是不对的，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47307</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没有礼貌地和长辈对抗并不能成为一个领袖。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47307</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51592</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可是，是卢克先开始的啊，” 凯蒂说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51592</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54742</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们只是遵守我们的原则而已。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54742</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59979</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不过，那确实是有点儿没有礼貌。” 劳拉对乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61942</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61942</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66840</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>昨天，她无视柯提思老师时，感觉很有意思。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66840</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70804</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，今天她的感觉并不是很好。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76023</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们别聊学校的事了，今天可是星期五！” 卢克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76023</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80276</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“卢克说得对，星期五是个开心的日子！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80276</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>谁想去我们家池塘滑冰？” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88046</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇，一定会很有意思！” 奥利维亚说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88046</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94305</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可是，我们有家务要做，凯蒂，还有作业。” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94305</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97610</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她在想关于领袖的发表呢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97610</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99905</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂翻了个白眼，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99905</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天是星期五，家务和作业是星期六和星期天的任务。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105329</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108966</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们回家拿冰鞋。” 卡洛斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108966</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111773</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也是。” 卢克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111773</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114679</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快点儿啊，一定会很有趣的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114679</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂对她姐姐说，“求你了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118951</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121873</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊笑了。“好吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121873</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126204</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂是对的，星期五是玩耍的日子！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131113</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个小时后，大家都来到了多诺万家的池塘上滑冰。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131113</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“耶！看我！” 劳拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137722</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她单腿滑冰，还跳了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137722</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的这个动作会更酷！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140845</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卢克加速，然后侧滑，停了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148098</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我一直在练习旋转。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148098</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152874</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂单脚旋转，摇摇晃晃地转了一圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152874</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157026</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎哟！” 她喊了一声，摔倒在冰上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157026</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊笑着看朋友们在冰上表演特技。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161448</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166791</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呀，” 凯蒂说，“天要黑了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166791</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们该回家了。” 卡洛斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174424</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们家有个池塘，可真好。” 劳拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174424</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂和乔伊把朋友们送到车道上，挥手说再见。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182138</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，她们也回家了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182138</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184491</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等等。” 乔伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184491</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187941</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要去捡鸡蛋，再看看母鸡们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187941</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194675</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她来到鸡圈，母鸡们并在一起睡觉，挤在一起取暖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194675</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204810</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一、二、三、四、五。” 乔伊数了数，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204810</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207960</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“五只？还有一只不见了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207960</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212755</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊又快速地数了一遍，还是只有五只。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212755</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215414</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第六只母鸡在哪儿呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215414</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她查看了整个鸡圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221311</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有人偷走了吗？它怎么出去的呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221311</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊低着头走进了厨房。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229886</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈，凯蒂，我有一个坏消息。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229887</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233993</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么了，宝贝？” 妈妈转过头来问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233993</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236859</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她正在做意大利面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236859</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240276</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一只鸡没了。” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240276</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243438</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么会没了呢？” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243438</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，她倒吸了一口冷气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246584</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等等，你是说死了一只鸡？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251728</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251728</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256984</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不过今天早上鸡圈里有六只，现在只有五只了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262210</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊安静地说，“我是一个坏学生、一个坏领袖，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262210</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268089</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>也是一个坏养鸡人。爷爷肯定对我很失望。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268089</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270225</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会帮你找的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270225</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂用一只胳膊搂着乔伊说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看了一眼漆黑的窗外，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278729</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“明天。” 她补充说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278729</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281531</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也会帮你的。” 妈妈说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281531</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285948</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“再说，谁知道呢？也许母鸡会自己出来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285948</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288471</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈也搂住了乔伊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288471</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294750</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>多诺万家的三个女人站在窗前，注视着漆黑的窗外。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294750</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298761</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>外面的风很大，今晚显得格外的寒冷。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298761</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304580</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么我去滑冰了而没有去查看母鸡呢？” 乔伊自问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304580</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307618</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，迷路的母鸡！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314200</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不论你在哪里，我都希望你能平安，暖和。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>